  "None suggested yet": "Ei vielä ehdotuksia",
  "After the AI responds, a separate quiet API call generates the tracker JSON independently. Expect ~250–300s total per message (narrative + wait + tracker).": "Vastauksen jälkeen hiljainen kutsu luo JSON:in. ~250–300s/viesti.",
  "✓ Single API call — typically ~100–120s total": "✓ Yksi API-kutsu — ~100–120s",
